{"tid":2240310,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"史上最佳員工","createTime":"2020-10-12T14:32:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T23:51:06.000Z","uid":235597,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"83936e041e813fbf465d78fd703a15a5a959935c","tid":2240310,"uid":235597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T14:32:47.000Z","msg":"今日已經係比公司拖糧既第<span class=\"xx-large\">六</span>個月<br />\n部分同事直情拖足<span class=\"xx-large\">八</span>個月<br />\n首先要表揚一下未餓死嘅我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然疫情直接影響到公司<br />\n但共患難都半年，重唔出真係有啲離譜<br />\n每次追數重要我好尷尬，明明啲錢係自己嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲同事都唔出聲，因為積埋好多claim錢未拎返怕拎唔到，又有同事依然忠心耿耿比人洗撚左腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同佢傾出糧好似殺左佢老豆老母，希望其他依然清醒嘅同事企硬，祝我哋早日收齊人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家唔洗建議我去勞工處，因為公司啲嘢一文不值，清盤都賣唔到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />費事攬炒咁多位同事既人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位同事如果聽日八號波打唔成又可以公司見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e91770f012ddf2a5a4f3f7a8c29245a993a9b75","tid":2240310,"uid":104804,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T14:34:46.000Z","msg":"貼錢打工<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb43fed333cec70381665af35de15fbab393479","tid":2240310,"uid":46013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T14:35:25.000Z","msg":"唔告？"},{"pid":"364c7dc8ae3bc83d86242c1aa8a976d504fb44eb","tid":2240310,"uid":7332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T14:36:08.000Z","msg":"開名"},{"pid":"eb10f01e7d7ff04a25c465a43b6317823a209a16","tid":2240310,"uid":252142,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T14:36:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4396f5db427e90a6f58834c5ca900d63f25bc20","tid":2240310,"uid":